Dianne Wiest

Birthday:
1948-03-28
Birthplace:
Kansas City, Missouri, United States

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Dianne Wiest (born March 28, 1948) is an American actress. She has had a successful career on stage, television, and film, and has won two Academy Awards, two Emmy Awards and a Golden Globe Award. Wiest has also been nominated for a BAFTA Award.
